WEBVTT

00:00:10.355 --> 00:00:14.285
Didn't know Deputy Phakphum
played politics too.

00:00:14.645 --> 00:00:15.845
My apologies

00:00:16.095 --> 00:00:18.205
for having my men bring you here like this.

00:00:19.165 --> 00:00:21.245
Well, you wouldn't pick up any
of my calls, Deputy.

00:00:24.235 --> 00:00:28.325
Billionaire Property is the one
buying up your old neighborhood.

00:00:28.445 --> 00:00:29.765
Do you know who the original owner was?

00:00:30.355 --> 00:00:32.325
Thaddao Mahasapkijboriboon.

00:00:32.525 --> 00:00:35.205
Burin’s common-law wife.

00:00:35.465 --> 00:00:36.765
That’s strange, though.

00:00:37.165 --> 00:00:39.925
Vicky never mentioned
being close to your family.

00:00:44.955 --> 00:00:46.325
No more patients for today, Doctor.

00:00:46.515 --> 00:00:49.685
But you have a surgery at 8 PM,
filling in for Dr. Chu.

00:00:51.145 --> 00:00:51.685
Got it.

00:00:51.825 --> 00:00:54.845
- Can you order dinner for me then?
- Sure.

00:01:00.075 --> 00:01:01.845
But as for dessert.

00:01:02.395 --> 00:01:04.965
I guess you don't need to order any.

00:01:17.955 --> 00:01:19.885
Enjoy your meal, Doctor.

00:01:25.795 --> 00:01:27.085
Damn it, Pete.

00:01:27.595 --> 00:01:29.605
You’re making everyone misunderstand us.

00:01:30.865 --> 00:01:32.405
Let them think what they want.
I don't care.

00:01:33.395 --> 00:01:34.805
Just as long as you don't
misunderstand me.

00:01:35.545 --> 00:01:37.765
Because if you weren't
a key witness in a major case,

00:01:38.355 --> 00:01:40.365
I wouldn't be sitting here
guarding you day and night.

00:01:40.915 --> 00:01:42.325
Sure, Mr. Handsome.

00:01:45.925 --> 00:01:49.685
Thanks. I never knew you could be...

00:01:50.155 --> 00:01:52.085
this kind to your key witness.

00:01:52.945 --> 00:01:54.205
Call me Sugar Daddy, kiddo.

00:01:56.595 --> 00:01:58.085
My daily motivation.

00:02:04.275 --> 00:02:06.525
Oh, by the way,
have you talked to Tarn lately?

00:02:08.035 --> 00:02:08.765
Nope.

00:02:10.565 --> 00:02:12.045
I sent her a text, but she didn't reply.

00:02:12.995 --> 00:02:14.205
She’s been ghosting me too.

00:02:19.755 --> 00:02:20.845
Don't bother calling her.

00:02:21.875 --> 00:02:23.605
Just let her enjoy her vacation for once.

00:02:24.755 --> 00:02:26.565
Let her spend some time with Ms. Vicky.

00:02:37.825 --> 00:02:39.085
Why are you holding my hand?

00:02:40.715 --> 00:02:41.845
Do you have feelings for me
or something?

00:02:43.805 --> 00:02:44.565
Nope.

00:02:45.635 --> 00:02:48.805
You just about to call Tarn.
I was only stopping you.

00:02:49.635 --> 00:02:50.805
I thought we were on the same page.

00:02:51.155 --> 00:02:52.485
Huh? What?

00:02:53.355 --> 00:02:54.085
Huh?

00:04:33.075 --> 00:04:33.805
You.

00:04:42.625 --> 00:04:45.005
Stay inside the house.
Don't go anywhere yet.

00:04:48.595 --> 00:04:50.645
Ken’s team is on their way
and will be here soon.

00:04:54.195 --> 00:04:55.325
What else is there?

00:04:55.835 --> 00:04:57.445
What else don't I know about you yet?

00:05:00.885 --> 00:05:02.085
I already told you.

00:05:02.955 --> 00:05:05.045
I'll tell you everything once this is over.

00:05:06.025 --> 00:05:07.725
But we're out of time right now.

00:05:08.115 --> 00:05:09.925
- If you...
- It’s always No, no, no.

00:05:10.835 --> 00:05:13.165
I ask you things,
and you tell me nothing.

00:05:14.995 --> 00:05:16.925
If you're going to handle
everything on your own like this,

00:05:17.945 --> 00:05:20.685
Then pretend you don't know me
and just get out of my life.

00:05:24.075 --> 00:05:24.885
You.

00:05:26.225 --> 00:05:28.885
The most important thing right now
is the Deputy’s life.

00:05:30.285 --> 00:05:31.885
Let me go save him first.

00:05:32.475 --> 00:05:34.485
When I get back,
I’ll tell you everything.

00:05:44.675 --> 00:05:46.525
You? You're going to help my father?

00:05:47.075 --> 00:05:49.005
I heard it with my own two ears.

00:05:49.975 --> 00:05:51.925
That you want revenge on him.

00:05:55.315 --> 00:05:56.165
You.

00:05:58.435 --> 00:05:59.725
I’m begging you.

00:06:00.755 --> 00:06:02.005
I’m begging you.

00:06:03.805 --> 00:06:05.445
Trust me one more time.

00:06:08.235 --> 00:06:09.525
Just this once.

00:06:13.275 --> 00:06:14.485
Trust me, okay?

00:07:37.955 --> 00:07:39.525
Hello, Captain Tara.

00:07:42.675 --> 00:07:43.925
I said, give me the gun!

00:07:44.125 --> 00:07:45.885
Or I'll blow your head off.

00:07:48.875 --> 00:07:50.125
You think I won't do it?

00:07:50.875 --> 00:07:51.645
Hand it over!

00:07:53.155 --> 00:07:53.885
One.

00:07:55.195 --> 00:07:55.965
Two.

00:07:59.315 --> 00:08:00.445
I told you to give it to me!

00:08:06.835 --> 00:08:08.685
A woman as beautiful
and capable as you,

00:08:09.835 --> 00:08:11.605
really shouldn't have to
face something like this.

00:08:17.275 --> 00:08:19.085
You're just as much of a scumbag
as your father was.

00:08:19.875 --> 00:08:21.725
If you hadn't played hard
to get that night.

00:08:22.355 --> 00:08:25.485
You could've been the lady
of this house by now.

00:08:28.515 --> 00:08:29.205
Go.

00:08:30.755 --> 00:08:31.885
Keep moving, I said!

00:08:41.915 --> 00:08:42.765
Move it!

00:08:57.425 --> 00:08:58.405
Thanks.

00:08:59.755 --> 00:09:02.245
For coming alone,
just like I requested.

00:09:05.715 --> 00:09:07.445
I’ve brought what you wanted.

00:09:23.195 --> 00:09:24.405
Hello.

00:09:27.115 --> 00:09:28.045
What are you looking at?

00:09:28.405 --> 00:09:31.325
Oh, I just found this album.

00:09:34.125 --> 00:09:35.125
Where’s the Deputy?

00:10:02.115 --> 00:10:03.205
Honestly,

00:10:05.035 --> 00:10:06.725
Why are you risking
your life like this, Captain?

00:10:07.435 --> 00:10:10.845
Why didn't you just give
this evidence to Commander Praken?

00:10:11.115 --> 00:10:13.525
And throw Phakphum and me in jail,

00:10:13.995 --> 00:10:15.605
just like you wanted?

00:10:17.555 --> 00:10:18.805
Or is it because...

00:10:20.795 --> 00:10:23.325
you’ve actually fallen
for Phakphum’s daughter?

00:10:38.345 --> 00:10:41.325
Loving the daughter of the man
who betrayed your own father?

00:10:43.555 --> 00:10:46.205
You only know that
your father fell to his death.

00:10:47.795 --> 00:10:48.965
But you have no idea.

00:10:49.395 --> 00:10:50.685
What really happened.

00:10:59.555 --> 00:11:00.445
Have a seat.

00:11:01.925 --> 00:11:04.965
I'll tell you exactly what Phakphum did.

00:11:06.845 --> 00:11:07.645
Sit down.

00:11:08.645 --> 00:11:09.845
I said, sit down!

00:11:21.115 --> 00:11:24.405
I bet that MP Burin is
going to have a hard time.

00:11:24.575 --> 00:11:26.285
Because we won't back down.

00:11:26.435 --> 00:11:28.245
No one is willing to sell their land to them.

00:11:29.755 --> 00:11:30.605
Please, Inspector.

00:11:31.355 --> 00:11:32.925
We’re counting on you to help us.

00:11:37.385 --> 00:11:40.285
I'm heading out to do some shopping,
then I'll pick up our kid on the way.

00:11:40.405 --> 00:11:41.045
Alright.

00:11:44.395 --> 00:11:46.605
You have to help us, Inspector.

00:11:47.195 --> 00:11:51.325
I believe if we can just kick MP Burin out,

00:11:51.595 --> 00:11:54.045
Everything will go back to the way it was.

00:11:58.605 --> 00:11:59.965
Stop fighting, Thana.

00:12:00.855 --> 00:12:02.485
You’re fighting a losing battle.

00:12:04.005 --> 00:12:06.285
Just sell the building,
take the money,

00:12:06.755 --> 00:12:08.925
and move your family
somewhere else to start over.

00:12:11.115 --> 00:12:12.325
Even if you’re getting lowballed,

00:12:12.435 --> 00:12:14.645
it’s still better than trading your life for it.

00:12:16.755 --> 00:12:19.285
Think about your wife and kid.
Keep them in mind.

00:12:22.595 --> 00:12:24.485
I thought you were a cop.

00:12:25.595 --> 00:12:26.565
Turns out,

00:12:27.795 --> 00:12:29.765
you’re just one of them.

00:12:30.445 --> 00:12:31.445
Get out!

00:12:32.085 --> 00:12:33.085
Get out!

00:12:33.805 --> 00:12:34.965
Get out!

00:12:44.315 --> 00:12:45.405
I'm worried about you.

00:12:46.195 --> 00:12:47.285
Get out!

00:12:48.115 --> 00:12:49.205
Get out!

00:12:51.155 --> 00:12:52.205
Get out!

00:12:53.885 --> 00:12:54.885
Get out!

00:12:55.565 --> 00:12:57.525
Get out of my house right now!

00:12:57.685 --> 00:12:58.805
Get out!

00:12:59.875 --> 00:13:01.525
You dirty cops!

00:13:01.805 --> 00:13:03.245
You're all the same. All of you.

00:13:03.805 --> 00:13:05.325
Siding with the rich.

00:13:05.595 --> 00:13:07.925
Scum. Absolute scum.

00:13:12.325 --> 00:13:13.805
You and your father are exactly the same.

00:13:14.355 --> 00:13:15.605
Just as stubborn.

00:13:16.745 --> 00:13:19.485
If he had sold the building properly,
your family would be comfortable by now.

00:13:20.555 --> 00:13:22.325
You and your mother
wouldn't have to suffer.

00:13:23.725 --> 00:13:26.005
And that stupid
anti-capitalist idealism of his.

00:13:27.595 --> 00:13:30.325
That's why I had to find a way
to get rid of him.

00:13:31.795 --> 00:13:33.205
Don't be afraid.

00:13:33.885 --> 00:13:35.365
We're in this fight together.

00:13:35.995 --> 00:13:37.525
I've already made the flyers.

00:13:37.995 --> 00:13:39.525
I'm going to head out
and hand them out now.

00:13:39.805 --> 00:13:41.925
Alright? See you tomorrow.

00:14:29.985 --> 00:14:30.845
You know what?

00:14:32.345 --> 00:14:35.725
Not only did he send
the evidence to Phakphum.

00:14:36.635 --> 00:14:38.485
But he even organized a mob
to come after me.

00:14:39.595 --> 00:14:41.285
He thought he was smart.

00:14:42.835 --> 00:14:44.205
But in reality, he was a fool.

00:14:44.775 --> 00:14:47.565
To underestimate
my money and my power.

00:14:48.355 --> 00:14:49.045
Hey!

00:14:49.835 --> 00:14:51.485
But things have changed now.

00:14:52.555 --> 00:14:54.085
our power is slipping away.

00:14:54.555 --> 00:14:56.485
The opposition is closing in on you.

00:14:57.235 --> 00:14:59.365
People's eyes are wide open now.

00:15:00.315 --> 00:15:02.405
That's why you resorted to
silencing them to destroy the evidence.

00:15:03.245 --> 00:15:04.605
Even if you kill me,

00:15:05.155 --> 00:15:06.285
or the Deputy.

00:15:07.915 --> 00:15:10.245
You can't hide your wickedness anymore.

00:15:11.755 --> 00:15:13.845
You think if you and Phakphum die,

00:15:14.045 --> 00:15:15.365
I won't survive?

00:15:20.235 --> 00:15:21.965
Let me tell you something.

00:15:23.315 --> 00:15:25.925
I never actually intended
to kill you, Captain."

00:15:27.995 --> 00:15:29.645
But I want you to kill him.

00:16:06.795 --> 00:16:09.845
My men threw your father off that rooftop.

00:16:11.205 --> 00:16:14.925
But the one who faked the evidence
to make it look like suicide

00:16:15.275 --> 00:16:16.565
was this cop right here.

00:16:22.755 --> 00:16:24.405
Look at him now—powerful
and high-ranking.

00:16:25.345 --> 00:16:26.405
And what about your father?

00:16:27.705 --> 00:16:29.365
He died like a dog in the street.

00:16:34.235 --> 00:16:36.925
And you’re still going to let him live?

00:16:38.265 --> 00:16:38.925
Hmm.

00:17:06.755 --> 00:17:07.645
Kill him.

00:17:09.235 --> 00:17:10.925
Let's be on the same side.

00:17:12.035 --> 00:17:13.205
Betray him.

00:17:13.835 --> 00:17:15.765
Just like he betrayed your father.

00:17:16.435 --> 00:17:17.805
hat's only fair.

00:17:24.075 --> 00:17:24.965
Pick up the gun.

00:17:30.635 --> 00:17:32.005
I said, pick it up!

00:17:45.635 --> 00:17:46.645
Shoot.

00:18:13.515 --> 00:18:14.245
Hey!

00:18:15.285 --> 00:18:17.045
I knew it, you scumbag.

00:18:18.275 --> 00:18:18.925
You bastard!

00:18:52.485 --> 00:18:53.565
Hey! Stop!

00:19:16.675 --> 00:19:20.005
I used to think Vicky was
such an innocent girl.

00:19:20.995 --> 00:19:22.285
But the truth is

00:19:22.955 --> 00:19:23.885
She’s far from innocent.

00:19:24.595 --> 00:19:26.005
This is what you call being stupid.

00:19:26.835 --> 00:19:29.845
Asking for death,
and dragging others down.

00:19:32.395 --> 00:19:33.565
Drop the gun!

00:19:34.835 --> 00:19:36.165
I said, drop it!

00:20:12.355 --> 00:20:13.045
Stop!

00:20:23.755 --> 00:20:24.605
Pa.

00:20:26.675 --> 00:20:28.645
Pa, Help me!

00:20:33.965 --> 00:20:34.805
Pa.

00:20:37.155 --> 00:20:37.965
Pa.

00:20:51.675 --> 00:20:52.765
Get him out of here!

00:20:54.595 --> 00:20:55.405
Go!

00:20:56.165 --> 00:20:56.885
Let's go.

00:20:57.315 --> 00:20:57.925
Hey.

00:21:04.955 --> 00:21:05.685
Go.

00:21:07.715 --> 00:21:08.725
Go!

00:21:10.235 --> 00:21:11.045
Let's go.

00:21:39.515 --> 00:21:40.125
Chai.

00:21:42.715 --> 00:21:43.405
Chai.

00:21:44.915 --> 00:21:46.045
Release him.

00:21:48.955 --> 00:21:49.725
Let him go.

00:22:36.675 --> 00:22:38.165
It's over, Captain.

00:23:01.235 --> 00:23:01.925
Go.

00:24:52.195 --> 00:24:53.165
Drop your weapons.

00:25:03.765 --> 00:25:04.765
Drop the gun.

00:25:05.645 --> 00:25:06.365
Drop it!

00:25:07.355 --> 00:25:08.445
Take them all into custody.

00:25:29.425 --> 00:25:29.965
Go.

00:25:30.085 --> 00:25:30.885
Keep moving.

00:25:31.515 --> 00:25:32.445
Lieutenant, get them in the car.

00:25:32.835 --> 00:25:33.445
Go.

00:25:34.475 --> 00:25:35.205
Get in.

00:25:37.235 --> 00:25:37.925
Sir.

00:25:38.725 --> 00:25:40.365
Please get some rest tonight, Sir.

00:25:40.765 --> 00:25:42.725
I'll pick you up tomorrow
for further statements.

00:25:43.955 --> 00:25:45.565
And what about Captain Tara?

00:25:48.995 --> 00:25:50.365
Let's go home, Dad.

00:25:56.355 --> 00:25:57.045
Get in.

00:26:26.355 --> 00:26:27.165
Thank you.

00:26:56.155 --> 00:26:56.885
Captain.

00:26:58.365 --> 00:26:59.325
Captain Pete!

00:26:59.725 --> 00:27:01.005
Captain Tara’s been shot!

00:27:01.405 --> 00:27:02.005
What?

00:27:04.555 --> 00:27:06.525
Tarn! Where were you hit?

00:27:08.075 --> 00:27:08.885
Tarn.

00:27:10.035 --> 00:27:11.325
Tarn, stay with me.

00:27:11.845 --> 00:27:12.845
Call an ambulance!

00:27:14.635 --> 00:27:15.765
Sometimes,

00:27:16.965 --> 00:27:19.045
the truth we’ve sacrificed everything for

00:27:19.955 --> 00:27:21.765
doesn’t really make anything better.

00:27:48.755 --> 00:27:50.725
I’ve disappointed you deeply, haven't I?

00:28:10.115 --> 00:28:12.085
I just don't know
how I'm supposed to feel anymore.

00:28:14.685 --> 00:28:18.525
Suddenly, everyone around me feels like a total stranger.

00:28:37.795 --> 00:28:38.845
I'm sorry.

00:28:43.155 --> 00:28:44.925
It all started with me.

00:28:47.355 --> 00:28:49.565
If only I hadn't abandoned my ideals.

00:28:51.125 --> 00:28:53.605
If I had stood by Thana until the very end,

00:28:56.315 --> 00:28:57.805
It wouldn't have come to this.

00:28:59.515 --> 00:29:01.485
Things would have turned out differently.

00:29:02.635 --> 00:29:03.765
- Honey.
- Hmm.

00:29:04.075 --> 00:29:05.365
There’s a delivery for you.

00:29:06.195 --> 00:29:06.925
Thanks.

00:29:26.805 --> 00:29:29.885
(Comply, unless you want
your family destroyed too.)

00:29:33.125 --> 00:29:36.525
(Comply, unless you want
your family destroyed too.)

00:29:56.245 --> 00:29:58.125
Thana chose to protect...

00:29:59.685 --> 00:30:01.125
his ideals,

00:30:02.485 --> 00:30:03.725
even if it cost him his life.

00:30:04.885 --> 00:30:06.045
But I...

00:30:08.075 --> 00:30:09.805
chose to abandon mine

00:30:10.995 --> 00:30:13.125
to protect my family.

00:30:15.915 --> 00:30:17.325
I know I did wrong.

00:30:20.075 --> 00:30:22.725
But back then,
there were no better options.

00:30:25.485 --> 00:30:26.365
At that time,

00:30:26.725 --> 00:30:28.325
I made a promise to myself.

00:30:28.805 --> 00:30:30.565
That I would stay alive

00:30:30.965 --> 00:30:33.645
until the day I had enough power

00:30:34.195 --> 00:30:36.485
to never bow to evil again

00:30:37.835 --> 00:30:39.565
and to be able to protect the good.

00:30:55.115 --> 00:30:57.845
I didn't keep the truth from you

00:30:58.955 --> 00:31:00.845
because I wanted to hide it.

00:31:03.275 --> 00:31:04.965
But any father

00:31:05.875 --> 00:31:07.565
would want to be a good man

00:31:08.675 --> 00:31:12.965
and a hero in the eyes of his own child.

00:31:17.315 --> 00:31:18.765
I’m sorry, Vicky.

00:31:19.355 --> 00:31:22.165
I’m truly sorry for letting you down.

00:31:33.435 --> 00:31:34.565
Do you know

00:31:36.035 --> 00:31:37.765
how many children

00:31:38.525 --> 00:31:40.685
have had their childhoods
stolen from them?

00:31:42.475 --> 00:31:44.005
They’re forced to grow up

00:31:44.285 --> 00:31:47.725
before they even understand the world.

00:31:50.995 --> 00:31:53.405
They have to force themselves
to be strong,

00:31:54.555 --> 00:31:55.845
even when they are...

00:31:56.715 --> 00:31:57.845
broken.

00:32:01.475 --> 00:32:02.685
One of them

00:32:03.685 --> 00:32:05.045
is Captain Tarn,

00:32:10.355 --> 00:32:11.845
your P'Looknam.

00:32:16.105 --> 00:32:18.485
She’s been through so much.

00:32:19.075 --> 00:32:21.925
She had to endure so much

00:32:23.675 --> 00:32:25.445
to grow into the fine person she is today.

00:32:28.665 --> 00:32:30.965
But the one person she has
always cared about

00:32:32.555 --> 00:32:33.805
is you.

00:32:36.965 --> 00:32:38.205
But in the end,

00:32:39.725 --> 00:32:42.005
There must have been a reason

00:32:43.395 --> 00:32:45.205
that brought her back here.

00:32:48.925 --> 00:32:52.005
If there’s anyone
who deserves your hatred.

00:32:52.955 --> 00:32:54.525
That person is me.

00:32:55.435 --> 00:32:56.765
Not P'Looknam.

00:33:22.195 --> 00:33:23.125
How is she doing?

00:33:23.285 --> 00:33:24.325
Everything is stable.

00:33:24.645 --> 00:33:25.885
Her blood pressure is normal.

00:33:26.115 --> 00:33:27.685
Her pulse is stable.

00:33:28.165 --> 00:33:28.965
Thank you.

00:33:37.555 --> 00:33:38.845
Tarn.

00:33:51.355 --> 00:33:52.205
Tarn.

00:33:56.715 --> 00:33:57.685
Are you feeling dizzy?

00:34:01.355 --> 00:34:02.885
How many days have I been out?

00:34:06.435 --> 00:34:08.485
Two days and two nights.

00:34:10.325 --> 00:34:10.845
Whoa!

00:34:11.045 --> 00:34:11.885
Tarn.

00:34:12.075 --> 00:34:13.165
Don't get up yet.

00:34:14.195 --> 00:34:15.205
Slowly now.

00:34:16.155 --> 00:34:17.325
Does it hurt?

00:34:18.075 --> 00:34:20.045
Don’t move yet,
or your stitches might rip.

00:34:21.045 --> 00:34:21.965
Ouch!

00:34:31.715 --> 00:34:33.605
Didn't anyone come to visit me at all?

00:34:35.205 --> 00:34:37.045
If you mean the Chief
and the guys from the unit,

00:34:37.275 --> 00:34:39.245
they’ve been taking turns
dropping by in the evenings.

00:34:39.685 --> 00:34:42.605
As for Pete,
he’s here whenever he's free.

00:34:42.765 --> 00:34:44.165
You know how he is.

00:34:44.995 --> 00:34:47.645
But if you’re asking about Vicky.

00:34:53.115 --> 00:34:54.765
Ever since she found out you were shot,

00:34:55.165 --> 00:34:58.165
she stayed outside the OR
until you were out of the woods.

00:34:59.955 --> 00:35:01.245
Once you were moved to this room,

00:35:01.385 --> 00:35:03.645
she stayed by your side day and night.

00:35:03.845 --> 00:35:05.525
She didn't sleep at all
until she eventually fainted.

00:35:09.025 --> 00:35:11.285
I just forced her
to go home this morning.

00:35:13.155 --> 00:35:14.525
Is she okay?

00:35:17.385 --> 00:35:19.165
Just exhaustion and low blood pressure.

00:35:25.835 --> 00:35:26.605
Look,

00:35:27.915 --> 00:35:29.565
if you’re that worried about her

00:35:29.725 --> 00:35:31.525
then hurry up and get well
so you can go make it up to her.

00:35:31.765 --> 00:35:33.885
The one who should be feeling hurt here

00:35:34.005 --> 00:35:36.005
is Vicky, not you.

00:35:36.315 --> 00:35:37.205
You tough.

00:35:39.635 --> 00:35:40.765
I get it already.

00:35:45.035 --> 00:35:45.885
Let's me see.

00:35:51.075 --> 00:35:55.685
- Tarn! Tarn’s awake!
- Hey, Pete!

00:35:56.555 --> 00:35:58.965
Stop shaking her!
You're gonna rip her stitches open!

00:35:59.075 --> 00:36:00.765
Oh, come on! She’s fine.

00:36:00.865 --> 00:36:02.965
Look at those eyes clear
as a healthy fish!

00:36:03.055 --> 00:36:03.605
Stop.

00:36:03.765 --> 00:36:04.885
- What?
- Ugh, stop!

00:36:05.635 --> 00:36:06.885
Can you guys please stop arguing?

00:36:07.125 --> 00:36:08.045
You’re the one doing it!

00:36:08.945 --> 00:36:11.565
Hey, Tarn.
I’ve got something to tell you.

00:36:11.945 --> 00:36:13.885
- The day you...
- Why are you sitting there?

00:36:14.325 --> 00:36:15.005
Huh?

00:36:15.295 --> 00:36:17.205
That day you went to the beach with Vicky,

00:36:17.915 --> 00:36:20.125
Deputy Phakphum
came to see P'Ken at the unit.

00:36:21.895 --> 00:36:24.005
What? Why was he there?

00:36:25.955 --> 00:36:27.325
This is all the evidence

00:36:27.725 --> 00:36:30.685
of how Minister Burin staged
the attempt on my life.

00:36:30.995 --> 00:36:34.445
I see your unit is handling
Director Dilok’s shooting.

00:36:35.345 --> 00:36:38.245
and the protest leader's
abduction and murder last year.

00:36:38.525 --> 00:36:40.365
I want you to take on my case.

00:36:40.835 --> 00:36:43.405
I’ve already consulted with
the Police Commissioner about this.

00:36:44.195 --> 00:36:45.885
Are these cases linked, sir?

00:36:46.555 --> 00:36:48.205
The motive is exactly the same.

00:36:49.355 --> 00:36:52.045
Every victim held a secret over Mr. Burin.

00:36:53.125 --> 00:36:56.645
Director Dilok was the one who approved
the hospital’s new building project.

00:36:56.995 --> 00:36:59.685
As for the student protest leader,

00:36:59.925 --> 00:37:04.325
they had evidence of Mr. Burin’s
corruption over the past decade.

00:37:04.915 --> 00:37:05.925
And as for me,

00:37:06.565 --> 00:37:09.685
I have evidence of
Mr. Burin’s land grabbing...

00:37:09.845 --> 00:37:11.725
nearly twenty years ago,

00:37:13.545 --> 00:37:15.525
and the murder of
a property owner back then.

00:37:16.235 --> 00:37:18.045
Then why is he still walking free?

00:37:18.995 --> 00:37:20.645
Especially since the case
reached your hands.

00:37:21.195 --> 00:37:22.365
Because I...

00:37:23.035 --> 00:37:24.205
let it slide.

00:37:27.315 --> 00:37:28.525
You realize, don't you?

00:37:30.475 --> 00:37:32.005
That once we start this

00:37:33.835 --> 00:37:35.645
it won't just be
Mr. Burin who goes down.

00:37:38.205 --> 00:37:39.445
Just think about it.

00:37:40.315 --> 00:37:44.525
Deputy Phakphum could have teamed up
with that deadly father-son duo anytime.

00:37:45.035 --> 00:37:46.045
But this time,

00:37:46.955 --> 00:37:48.765
he’s actually putting justice first.

00:37:54.845 --> 00:37:57.565
The list of charges against
Minister Burin is a mile long.

00:37:58.515 --> 00:38:00.445
The attempted murders of
Deputy Phakphhum,

00:38:00.715 --> 00:38:01.805
Director Dilok,

00:38:02.155 --> 00:38:03.405
and many others.

00:38:04.355 --> 00:38:07.005
Even the case of masterminding
my father’s murder 20 years ago

00:38:07.275 --> 00:38:09.165
is being reopened.

00:38:10.435 --> 00:38:12.605
And as for Boworntat,
he’s just as bad as his father.

00:38:13.165 --> 00:38:16.365
Charged with the murder and
concealment of Dr. Anya’s body.

00:38:17.355 --> 00:38:21.005
Plus money laundering
and multiple drug charges.

00:38:22.115 --> 00:38:24.285
Due to the high profile nature of the crimes,

00:38:24.455 --> 00:38:27.565
the father and son were denied bail
and immediately taken into custody.

00:38:28.685 --> 00:38:32.805
Deputy Commissioner Phakphum has been
suspended pending investigation.

00:38:34.155 --> 00:38:36.325
Now, he is just an ordinary man.

00:38:37.165 --> 00:38:38.525
No entourage.

00:38:39.445 --> 00:38:41.205
No status to maintain.

00:38:46.465 --> 00:38:49.365
You realize, don't you?
That once we start this

00:38:51.205 --> 00:38:52.925
it won't just be
Mr. Burin who goes down.

00:38:53.205 --> 00:38:54.325
If I am to die,

00:38:54.845 --> 00:38:57.885
I don't want to die as a man
who betrayed his profession

00:38:58.235 --> 00:39:00.125
and his homeland.

00:39:23.915 --> 00:39:24.845
Thanks.

00:39:49.185 --> 00:39:50.925
I'm sorry, Looknam.

00:40:15.475 --> 00:40:16.565
Sometimes,

00:40:17.195 --> 00:40:18.925
admitting our mistakes

00:40:19.905 --> 00:40:21.765
is the bravest thing...

00:40:22.525 --> 00:40:24.365
a person can do.

00:41:29.035 --> 00:41:30.605
I’m moving to the countryside.

00:41:30.845 --> 00:41:32.485
We won’t be seeing
each other anymore.

00:41:32.955 --> 00:41:34.685
Will you be okay without me?

00:41:39.265 --> 00:41:41.605
And P'Looknam...

00:41:42.125 --> 00:41:43.845
where are you moving to?

00:41:58.915 --> 00:42:00.965
This is my Goodnight doll.

00:42:02.155 --> 00:42:04.205
I hug it every single night.

00:42:04.795 --> 00:42:08.045
Mom told me that if I can’t sleep,

00:42:08.645 --> 00:42:10.325
I should just give it a hug.

00:42:10.875 --> 00:42:11.965
Here, this is for you.

00:42:16.655 --> 00:42:19.005
Because when we grow up,

00:42:19.435 --> 00:42:21.365
and we can’t recognize
each other anymore.

00:42:21.915 --> 00:42:23.085
But if...

00:42:23.485 --> 00:42:27.165
I see who has this doll,

00:42:27.675 --> 00:42:30.485
I’ll know that person is you, P'Looknam.

00:42:31.325 --> 00:42:32.405
Thank you.

00:42:54.955 --> 00:42:55.925
Nong Noo.

00:43:24.595 --> 00:43:25.885
Why didn’t you tell me

00:43:27.075 --> 00:43:28.245
who you really were?

00:43:30.995 --> 00:43:32.685
Even though you had so many chances.

00:43:35.585 --> 00:43:37.725
If I had told you
before knowing the whole truth,

00:43:41.955 --> 00:43:43.565
everything would have ended right then.

00:43:44.085 --> 00:43:45.645
But I wasn’t happy

00:43:46.525 --> 00:43:47.485
not even once

00:43:48.835 --> 00:43:50.165
having to hide it from you.

00:43:51.005 --> 00:43:52.805
I was scared every time I held you.

00:43:53.245 --> 00:43:54.365
I was so afraid.

00:43:59.395 --> 00:44:01.165
Afraid that if the truth came out,

00:44:04.235 --> 00:44:06.085
what we have would be over.

00:44:07.835 --> 00:44:09.005
I was just scared.

00:44:10.675 --> 00:44:12.285
Scared that you would hate me.

00:44:13.785 --> 00:44:15.965
But if I were to forget
what happened to my father,

00:44:19.205 --> 00:44:21.045
I’d be a disloyal daughter.

00:44:28.575 --> 00:44:31.045
I want to love you with all my heart.

00:44:37.435 --> 00:44:38.725
but I don't dare to.

00:44:43.915 --> 00:44:45.165
But as for not loving you.

00:44:51.345 --> 00:44:52.725
I just can't do it.

00:45:03.915 --> 00:45:05.125
Do you know?

00:45:06.155 --> 00:45:08.125
That when I found out
who you really were.

00:45:08.835 --> 00:45:10.605
Found out what my father had done.

00:45:12.195 --> 00:45:13.925
And what you've had to go through.

00:45:14.475 --> 00:45:16.085
I felt so guilty too.

00:45:23.235 --> 00:45:24.845
But you were still so good to me.

00:45:25.435 --> 00:45:27.165
Even though you knew everything all along.

00:45:31.595 --> 00:45:33.045
When you came to say goodbye,

00:45:36.405 --> 00:45:37.805
you weren't angry.

00:45:39.085 --> 00:45:41.005
You didn't hate me even a little bit, right?

00:45:45.835 --> 00:45:46.765
No.

00:45:48.595 --> 00:45:49.805
Never.

00:46:01.645 --> 00:46:03.965
How could I ever be angry with you?

00:46:10.715 --> 00:46:11.845
Don't cry.

00:46:30.035 --> 00:46:31.125
I'm sorry.

00:46:33.275 --> 00:46:35.085
I'm sorry for everything.

00:46:37.315 --> 00:46:38.845
I’m sorry for hiding the truth.

00:46:40.785 --> 00:46:42.365
I’m sorry for lying.

00:46:43.595 --> 00:46:45.405
I’m sorry for not telling you the truth.

00:46:46.505 --> 00:46:48.645
I’m sorry I wasn't there for you.

00:47:18.795 --> 00:47:20.605
Tarn told me
you’re going to study abroad.

00:47:22.155 --> 00:47:24.085
And you weren't even going to tell me?

00:47:25.075 --> 00:47:26.765
Why are you being so mean to me?

00:47:27.075 --> 00:47:28.845
I haven't even found a girlfriend yet.

00:47:29.785 --> 00:47:31.205
Well, that’s your problem, isn't it?

00:47:31.645 --> 00:47:33.885
Do I really have to stay just to
wait for you to get a girlfriend?

00:47:36.915 --> 00:47:38.605
On humanitarian grounds.

00:47:39.155 --> 00:47:40.165
Yes, you should.

00:47:40.565 --> 00:47:42.765
Because when you were a witness
in Dr. Anya’s case,

00:47:42.965 --> 00:47:44.565
I had to watch over you day and night.

00:47:44.685 --> 00:47:46.245
To the point where everyone thought
we were a couple!

00:47:47.195 --> 00:47:49.485
The reason I’m still single is
because of you.

00:47:50.105 --> 00:47:51.925
Even if you didn't have to watch over me,

00:47:52.305 --> 00:47:53.725
you’d still be single anyway.

00:47:53.995 --> 00:47:55.565
But I don't want you to go.

00:47:58.035 --> 00:47:58.965
Why?

00:48:04.675 --> 00:48:06.005
Because I like you!

00:48:10.675 --> 00:48:12.045
Pete!

00:48:12.875 --> 00:48:14.925
How can you be so selfish?

00:48:15.245 --> 00:48:16.685
Tarn already has Vicky,

00:48:16.875 --> 00:48:18.605
and I’ll have a girlfriend soon enough.

00:48:18.725 --> 00:48:20.285
You're just jealous!

00:48:25.555 --> 00:48:26.365
Fine.

00:48:27.245 --> 00:48:28.125
I am...

00:48:29.505 --> 00:48:31.045
actually afraid of you having a boyfriend.

00:48:32.475 --> 00:48:33.605
If you’re not around,

00:48:34.875 --> 00:48:36.205
I’m going to be so lonely.

00:48:37.975 --> 00:48:41.485
It’s not like
I’m leaving today or tomorrow.

00:48:43.945 --> 00:48:45.405
But you’ve already packed your bags.

00:48:49.315 --> 00:48:51.045
I’m just going to the beach.

00:48:52.315 --> 00:48:54.245
Vicky invited me.

00:48:54.485 --> 00:48:55.445
Then let me go too!

00:48:55.685 --> 00:48:56.445
No.

00:48:56.685 --> 00:48:57.405
Why not?

00:48:57.605 --> 00:48:58.685
She didn't invite you!

00:48:58.785 --> 00:48:59.925
Please let me go?

00:49:00.275 --> 00:49:01.485
- Please?
- No.

00:49:01.565 --> 00:49:02.725
Please.

00:49:02.955 --> 00:49:03.805
Are you gonna let me go?

00:49:05.275 --> 00:49:06.325
Let me go with you too.

00:49:07.035 --> 00:49:07.845
Please.

00:51:03.315 --> 00:51:04.525
Sleepyhead.

00:51:05.275 --> 00:51:06.805
Still not awake yet?

00:51:11.235 --> 00:51:13.805
Is that all the energy
you have to wake me up?

00:51:27.555 --> 00:51:29.205
How much energy do you want?

00:51:33.195 --> 00:51:34.765
That’s up to you.

00:51:43.795 --> 00:51:44.765
You said it.

00:52:14.955 --> 00:52:16.365
Here we go. Ready?

00:52:17.115 --> 00:52:18.325
That tickles!

00:52:20.555 --> 00:52:22.205
Come here, sleepyhead!

00:52:22.435 --> 00:52:23.925
You're picking on me again!

00:52:40.965 --> 00:52:41.805
You.

00:52:43.115 --> 00:52:44.125
Are you done yet?

00:52:44.765 --> 00:52:46.165
I'm hungry.

00:52:46.755 --> 00:52:48.125
Almost.

00:52:48.315 --> 00:52:50.085
You can go ahead and eat first.

00:52:50.875 --> 00:52:52.285
No thanks.

00:52:52.525 --> 00:52:53.885
I want to wait and eat with you.

00:53:30.715 --> 00:53:33.245
What is this?
When did you take this?

00:53:33.915 --> 00:53:36.165
No, I look terrible. Why this photo?

00:53:39.115 --> 00:53:40.125
Because...

00:53:41.175 --> 00:53:43.085
this photo was the beginning.

00:53:44.365 --> 00:53:47.005
The moment I stopped loving
you as just a little sister.

00:54:34.835 --> 00:54:35.965
I love you.

00:54:45.915 --> 00:54:47.485
I love you too.